Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝著傳說中的樂園——煌珠樂園進發的酷他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到了煌珠獵人臥魯克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.58,0:02:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向酷、希絲卡他們就守護翼的所作所為提出了質疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從人類社會中隔離起來加以保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是否會使煌珠們幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未得出結論的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.48,0:02:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一行人又朝著新的城市進發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.03,0:02:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.74,0:02:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉茲飛·安克魯港鎮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡著了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃點東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.91,0:02:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢 行李又都燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.34,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 要被你吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前...前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 不會忍耐的一幫傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.73,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之沒錢是生死攸關的大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既不能吃飯又不能住宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不想那樣的話就盡快到城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竭盡全力地工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.25,0:03:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.88,0:03:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 酷你們先去城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.49,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好地努力賺錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼就我們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這裏還有些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 就不能快點走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是守護翼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會讓你們去拉茲飛·安克魯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請就此回頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是衝著我們來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.45,0:04:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九唱 港鎮的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是接近城鎮就要來攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個危險的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來拉茲飛·安克魯這個城鎮裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.00,0:04:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隱藏著相當大的秘密不想讓我們知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向這位大人打聽一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼可以跟你們說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位大人雖然好像有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.30,0:04:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.15,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣規模的城鎮的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許可以知道去煌珠樂園的途徑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 不是沒錢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從小就當空賊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢要多少去偷不就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能做小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要說工作 我能做的好像...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定有酷能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能做的工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能做的工作 就這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 好好做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道蕾做得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.95,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫蕾 你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女 只要呼喚女神 機會就會降生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望著腳下之地 有著主的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就老老實實交代的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也就會更溫柔一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,探聽出了一個很大的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話一定得實際潛入城鎮進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.16,0:07:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這身裝束不是明擺著通知敵人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太狠毒了 那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.36,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼 就沒有天理了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰來救救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真過分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這家店就這麼招待顧客的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.85,0:08:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...但是您突然一下子站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不敢 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為陪禮能不能稍微陪我一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開 請放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 別太放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光天化日之下欺負女孩子取樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺不錯的愛好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小毛孩就一邊待著去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是吃飯的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種蟑螂就滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是煌珠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離莉莉雅遠點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼啊 突然這麼一下子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於想把莉莉雅帶走的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不會輕饒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.94,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點投降 別再靠近莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要稍微聽一下別人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.29,0:09:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受傷了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.01,0:09:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜...拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 請原諒我姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.32,0:11:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個既然你請求了當然就原諒她嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過能不能說說是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是煌珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.79,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說你姐姐也是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.61,0:11:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和拉撒蒂姐姐不是親姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是嬰兒的時候就被撿到 來到了姐姐家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.84,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收養我的爸爸媽媽非常和藹可親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.36,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在我們小時候兩個人都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.89,0:12:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸很老實 被人利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.56,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不覺欠下了很多債
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我差點要被人帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.66,0:12:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急關頭 教堂的瑪魯先生救了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.37,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪魯先生和借給父親錢的那些人進行了交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於談妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.31,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢並不用急著還 能一點點還清就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.24,0:13:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過說實話對方想要的是莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因為莉莉雅是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們改變了想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.96,0:13:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果說得到莉莉雅後就能去賣錢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知什麼時候會有野蠻人來搶走莉莉雅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一點點還就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,積攢下錢後就交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我來交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勸說他們不要打莉莉雅的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是 姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.81,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓我不用擔心會被誰帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.27,0:13:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡早讓我重獲自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做著危險的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我而跟別人打鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.18,0:14:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.97,0:14:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為你要把莉莉雅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.96,0:14:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是在剛懂事的時候父母去世的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天為了活下去就精疲力盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.79,0:14:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被老大收養成為空賊後有了很多朋友倒是過得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.62,0:14:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我也有點明白你想要保護莉莉雅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡她嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋 你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是和蕾說好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 帶蕾去她想去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.04,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像不是個壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像你說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不嫌棄的話今天就留下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錢的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.01,0:15:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉雅會準備飯菜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了 你們家也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺我們這樣反而更引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意 別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這城鎮上的煌珠似乎都在往同一個地方聚集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.19,0:16:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕那裏應該就是我們的目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.17,0:16:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白天發生了那樣的事 出入小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.06,0:16:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂是去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.99,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你一個人留在家裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去準備晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要呼喚女神 機會就會降生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望著腳下之地 有著主的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位紳士淑女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎來到歡喜與悲嘆的賭鬥場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.28,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜用生命和熱情 賭上財富和名譽盡情享樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家可別錯過賭鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城市的地下竟然會有這樣的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這樣的規模從事這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕後肯定與龐大的組織有牽連
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賭鬥即將展開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家請注視會場中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.56,0:18:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先要介紹的是我們賭鬥場的鋼之巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達·飛羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:18:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然為了賭鬥而將煌珠武器化戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.48,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在守護翼的管轄下讓這樣的事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.28,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這恐怕只靠我們是解決不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得和這裏的指揮官取得聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,採取徹底性的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來介紹的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們賭鬥場引以自豪的擁有無敗記錄的少虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂·地可蕾絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飯就快好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.04,0:19:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡他們怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.80,0:19:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是就讓我們賺錢 自己去遊玩了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.99,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你明白拉撒蒂的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.52,0:20:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷為什麼想要保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.67,0:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼盡出風頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才夠纏人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這次不會讓你搗亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是兩個人但又不是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.49,0:22:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為是兩個人所以想在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.29,0:22:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有的是一個真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.03,0:23:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 愛和慾望的賭鬥場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.45,0:23:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十唱 愛和慾望的賭鬥場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.10,0:23:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因為如此 少女們才苦惱

